A Conjuring Unleashes a Real Demon | 3 Demons | New Horror Conjuring Movie

Deputy sheriff Fisher, tasked with watching a corpse, unknowingly triggers a conjuring that leads to him becoming possessed. As his past is unearthed, he's forced to face his own demons with terrifying consequences.

2022 | Stars: Haley Benedict Heslip, Zoe Cunningham, Sherryl Despres
